36:01.726 --> 36:07.499 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so I think the idea here is
that he is
trying to see if there's any
chance of any

36:07.532 --> 36:10.602 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
opening on both sides to move
forward.

36:10.635 --> 36:17.075 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Is that complicated
by this Iranian
missile test? Obviously, Israel
has no love

36:17.108 --> 36:23.615 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
