36:27.118 --> 36:34.059 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DANIEL ESTRIN: Yes, this is one
of the main
issues looming over the vice
president's visit

36:34.092 --> 36:40.732 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in Israel, the Iranian deal and
specifically
what America is going to do for
Israel now.

36:40.765 --> 36:47.005 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And America promised Israel
