39:10.848 --> 39:16.054 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Daniel Estrin in
Jerusalem for
the Associated Press, thank you
so much.

39:16.087 --> 39:22.260 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DANIEL ESTRIN: You're welcome.

39:22.293 --> 39:30.602 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: We will be back to
